name: Wee Dolled Up
description:
This sweet graphic is perfect for your trendy styled tot!

Our super soft blend of organic cotton and bamboo fleece is machine washable and maintains a soft feel against baby's skin wash after wash.  Bamboo fleece has the softest hand of any fabric and is thick for maximum absorption.  A drool bib for the modern tot!

* 70% bamboo viscose fleece/30% organic cotton
* Highly waterproof, durable eco-friendly liner
* Hip graphics printed with durable, lead-free, phthalate free inks.
* 3-way adjustable snaps grows with your baby into toddler stage
* Burgandy contrast top stitching adds style and creates reinforcement 
* Low impact dyes
* Reversible
* Size: 11" x 12"

PATENT PENDING
Made in USA of imported and domestic fabrics

Each graphic design incorporates a recycle sign to reflect our company's effort in creating a greener world.
